data: The event "Software Engineer Interview" was conducted to assess a candidate's engineering skills and experience.
The event "Software Engineer Interview" included discussion of a high-traffic microservices system project led by the candidate.
The event "Software Engineer Interview" covered technologies such as Docker, Kubernetes, and AWS Lambda used in the candidate's project.
The event "Software Engineer Interview" addressed system reliability strategies implemented by the candidate, including circuit breakers and extensive monitoring.
The event "Software Engineer Interview" included discussion of diagnosing and patching a memory leak in a third-party library.
The event "Software Engineer Interview" concluded with an action item to schedule a follow-up technical task.
